// Test ta.stdev (Standard Deviation, population)
// Like Pine, na until the window has `length` bars. Over the last 3 bars close
// is 299, 300, 301: mean 300, variance 2/3, stdev sqrt(2/3).

// Bars: 3

sd = ta.stdev(close, 3)
log.info(str.tostring(sd))

// Expected output:
// NaN
// NaN
// 0.816496580927726
